OL,3,CSabastian Sawe receives hero's welcome
OL,4,Cin Kenya after London marathon triumph
OL,6,FSabastian Sawe received a hero's
OL,7,Fwelcome when he returned to Kenya on
OL,8,FWednesday after becoming the first
OL,9,Fperson ever to complete a marathon in
OL,10,Funder two hours at the London race
OL,11,Fover the weekend.
OL,13,FSawe was welcomed back to his country
OL,14,Fby his parents and Sports Minister
OL,15,FSalim Mvurya, who hailed the runner's
OL,16,Faccomplishment at the London Marathon
OL,17,Fas "a win for Kenya."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
