OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777546977
OL,3,CSabastian Sawe receives hero's welcome
OL,4,Cin Kenya after London marathon triumph
OL,6,FSawe, 31, pulled off the feat, long
OL,7,Fconsidered unthinkable, on Sunday when
OL,8,Fhe won in a time of 1 hour, 59
OL,9,Fminutes, 30 seconds. He beat the
OL,10,Fprevious men's world record by 65
OL,11,Fseconds.
OL,13,FBefore disembarking upon arrival at
OL,14,FNairobi's Jomo Kenyatta International
OL,15,FAirport, Sawe said he was proud to
OL,16,Fhave "made a great achievement in
OL,17,Flife" and was planning to "try and
OL,18,Flower the record further."
OL,20,FHe was adorned with a traditional
OL,21,Fwreath of twigs to symbolise victory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
