OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777546977
OL,3,CSabastian Sawe receives hero's welcome
OL,4,Cin Kenya after London marathon triumph
OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference, Sawe
OL,7,Fsaid: "I am happy to celebrate this
OL,8,Fwin with you. I didn't expect it would
OL,9,Fbe this way. I am very grateful.
OL,11,F"For everything we did in London, I
OL,12,Fdidn't do it for myself alone, I did
OL,13,Fit for all of us."
OL,15,FTraditional dancers sang his praises
OL,16,Fas he then climbed into a luxury
OL,17,Fgovernment vehicle as part of the
OL,18,F"heroic welcome" hailed by the sports
OL,19,Fminister, who said Sawe would be
OL,20,Fhonoured on Thursday.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
