OL,3,CSabastian Sawe receives hero's welcome
OL,4,Cin Kenya after London marathon triumph
OL,6,FHis coach, Claudio Berardelli, said he
OL,7,Fknew the athlete was in "extremely
OL,8,Fgood shape".
OL,10,F"I knew that maybe he could have run
OL,11,Ffast, but I was probably not expecting
OL,12,Fa sub-2 hours. But he was really in
OL,13,Fgood shape."
OL,15,FHis parents said they knew their son
OL,16,Fwas destined for greatness even as a
OL,17,Fchild, and his mother recounted how he
OL,18,Fsprinted during bath time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
