FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777546977
OL,3,CSabastian Sawe receives hero's welcome
OL,4,Cin Kenya after London marathon triumph
OL,6,F"He would run too fast. So, I would
OL,7,Fsay to myself, this boy will shine for
OL,8,Fme one day," Emily Sawe said.
OL,10,FHis father recounted watching Sunday's
OL,11,Fmarathon at his brother's house
OL,12,Fbecause his television lacked a clear
OL,13,Fsignal.
OL,15,F"The moment my son pulled in front, I
OL,16,Fwalked out and didn't see him finish
OL,17,Fthe race. I watched the replay
OL,18,Fafterwards. I was so happy, extremely
OL,19,Fhappy. We screamed so much that now it
OL,20,Fis hard to swallow anything," Simion
OL,21,FKiplagat Sawe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
