OL,3,CSabastian Sawe receives hero's welcome
OL,4,Cin Kenya after London marathon triumph
OL,6,FSawe was introduced to professional
OL,7,Frunning by his uncle, Abraham
OL,8,FChepkirwok, who ran the 800 meters for
OL,9,FUganda at the 2008 Beijing Olympics.
OL,11,FSawe won the Valencia Marathon in
OL,12,F2024, clocking 2:02:05. He went into
OL,13,FSunday's race in London as the
OL,14,Fdefending champion.
OL,16,FHis father said Sawe is disciplined
OL,17,Fand determined: "Even now, he still
OL,18,Fsays that record was not enough; he
OL,19,Fwants to lower it further."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
